info.author: Philip Jenvey
info.description: hellanzb is an easy to use app designed to retrieve nzb files and fully process them. The goal being to make getting files from Usenet as hands-free as possible. Once fully installed, all that's required is moving an nzb file to the queue directory. The rest: downloading, par-checking, un-raring, etc. is done automatically by hellanzb.
